1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,419
Good and evil are but the views of the majority. Morality is merely the consensus of society,

2
00:00:07,419 --> 00:00:14,560
ever-changing, easily manipulated, and deeply flawed. What one generation praises, the next

3
00:00:14,560 --> 00:00:21,960
may condemn. Why should I bind myself to such a fragile construct? I walk my own path,

4
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:29,480
one carved by my will and guided by my ambition. The cries of the world, their outrage and condemnation,

5
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:35,759
are nothing more than noise to me, futile attempts to enforce their illusions of order. Let them call

6
00:00:35,759 --> 00:00:43,359
me demon, devil, monster, it changes nothing. These labels are weapons of the weak, used to shackle

7
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:49,960
those with strength and vision, but I refuse to be chained. In the end only strength speaks

8
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:57,079
the truth. Only strength determines what is right, and I will become so strong the world itself

9
00:00:57,079 --> 00:01:01,280
will be forced to acknowledge me, whether it loves me or fears me.

